</ul>

<p><strong>Performance Metrics:</strong> Teams using Housecall Pro mobile see average invoice values increase by 18% due to the streamlined upselling workflow. Customer communication scores improve by 42% within 60 days of implementation.</p>

<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Starts at $61/month for 2 users. Payment processing at 2.9% + 25¢ per transaction.</p>

